Installing Cream in a Sandbox
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Installation
------------
For Ubuntu, do ::

    sudo apt-get install git-core python-virtualenv bzr cython libev-dev python-dev python-lxml python-webkit-dev libwebkit-dev
    git clone git://github.com/cream/cream
    cd cream/
    make setup

On other distros, please install the packages named above.


Joining the Sandbox
-------------------
To join the Cream sandbox, do ::

    source /path/to/cream/dev/bin/activate


Running stuff
-------------
After joining the sandbox, navigate to ``/path/to/cream/src/modules/`` and start modules, e.g. for Melange::

    cd melange
    python melange.py
